SUMMARY:The Check-In: A Jazz & Journaling Series
DTSTAMP:20260627T015258Z
DTSTART:20260627T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Check-In is an afternoon of movement\, meditation\, music\,
	 and journaling designed specifically for Black men.\n\nhttps://www.eventb
